The paper deals with nonrigid image registration, which is a topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of joint saliency map and adaptive kernel regression involves machine learning techniques (cs.AI, cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of superpixels, which is a topic in computer graphics (cs.GR) and the experimental results involve image processing (cs.MM).
